quran[14{c,v,t}:
23,105,""" kya tum wohi log nahi ho ke meri ayaat tumhe sunai jati theen to tum inhen jutlatay thay? """
23,106,"woh kahin ge"" ae hamaray rab, hamari bad bakhti hum par chhaa gayi thi waqai hum gumraah log thay"
23,107,"ae parvar-digaar, ab hamein yahan se nikaal day phir hum aisa qasoor karen to zalim hon ge """
23,108,"Allah taala jawab day ga"" daur ho mere samnay se, parre raho isi mein aur mujh se baat nah karo"
23,109,"tum wohi log to ho ke mere kuch bande jab kehte thay ke ae hamaray parvar-digaar, hum imaan laaye, hamein maaf kar day, hum par reham kar, Tu sab reahimon se acha Raheem hai"
23,110,"to tum ne un ka mazaq bana liya yahan taq ke unn ki zid ne tumhe yeh bhi bhula diya ke mein bhi koi hon, aur tum un par hanstay rahay"
23,111,"aaj unn ke uss sabr ka mein ne yeh phal diya hai ke wohi kamyaab hain """
23,112,"phir Allah taala un se pouchye ga"" batao, zameen mein tum kitney saal rahay? """
23,113,"woh kahin ge"" aik din ya din ka bhi kuch hissa hum wahan thire hain shumaar karne walon se pooch lijiye """
23,114,"irshad ho ga"" thori hi der thire ho na, kash tum ne yeh uss waqt jana hota"
23,115,"kya tum ne yeh samajh rakha tha ke hum ne tumhe fuzool hi peda kya hai aur tumhe hamari taraf kabhi palatna hi nahi hai? """
23,116,"pas baala o bartar hai Allah , Padasha haqeeqi, koi khuda uss ke siwa nahi, maalik hai arsh buzurag ka"
23,117,"aur jo koi Allah ke sath kisi aur mabood ko pukare, jis ke liye is ke paas koi Daleel nahi, to is ka hisaab is ke rab ke paas hai aisay kafir kabhi Falah nahi pa satke"
23,118,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, kaho,"" mere rab dar guzar farma, aur reham kar, aur to sab reahimon se acha Raheem hai """
